Descriptions.Description: Formulated with full-synthetic, premium base oils, long-life friction modifiers, unique anti-wear additives and shear stable viscosity modifiers that help prevent oil film breakdown. Recommended for use in the following CVT applications: Audi and VW (TL 52180 G 052 180), Ford (CVT30/Mercon C), Subaru (Lineartronic CVTF), Honda (HMMF), Nissan (NS-2), Mitsubishi (CVTF-J1/SP-III), BMW Mini Cooper EZL 799), Hyundai and Kia (SP-III), Suzuki (TC/NS-2/CVT Green1), Dodge, Jeep (NS-2/CVTF+4), GM Saturn (DEX-CVT), Ford (CVT23), and Mercedes Benz (236.20).
Formulated with full-synthetic base stocks and advanced additive technology to meet the challenging demands of CVT transmissions

Developed with anti-wear technology to help improve transmission durability
